            Rationl is a tool for experimentally investigating and fixing software issues.
        </p>
        <p>
            <a class="btn btn-lg btn-success" href="/authorize" role="button">Sign in with GitHub</a>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div> <!-- /container -->
  </body>
</html>
